openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  version: "1.2.3"
  title: "securitySchemes"
paths:
  /security-ko-put:
    put:
      responses: {}
  /security-ko-patch:
    patch:
      responses: {}
  /security-empty-ko-patch:
    patch:
      responses: {}
      security: []
  /security-explicit-ok-patch:
    patch:
      responses: {}
      security:
        - {}
  /security-ok:
    post:
      security:
        -  BasicAuth: []
      responses: {}
  /security-ko-get:
    get:
      responses: {}

components:
  securitySchemes:
    BasicAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: basic
    MyOauth_ko:
      type: oauth2
    MyOauth_ok:
      type: oauth2
      "flows":
        "authorizationCode":
          "authorizationUrl": "https://petstore3.swagger.io/oauth/authorize"
      description: |-
          The implementation of JWT conforms RFC8725.
    MyOauth2_ko:
      type: oauth2
      description: A blatant description
    JWTBearer_ko: &JWTBearer_ko
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: "JWT"
    JWTBearer2_ko:
      <<: *JWTBearer_ko
      description: a blatant description
    JWTBearer_ok:
      description: |-
        The implementation conforms RFC8725
        and uses only `EdDSA` RFC8032.
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: "JWT"
    MyOauth_ko3:
      type: oauth2
      description: The implementation of JWT conforms RFC8725.
      "flows":
        "authorizationCode":
          "authorizationUrl": "http://petstore3.swagger.io/oauth/authorize"
        "implicit":
          "authorizationUrl": "https://petstore3.swagger.io/oauth/authorize"
        "password":
          "authorizationUrl": "https://petstore3.swagger.io/oauth/authorize"
